        <relatedmaterial id="ref29">
            <head>Related Material at the New-York Historical Society</head>
            <p>The New-York Historical Society Library's Manuscript Department holds a collection of Fabres's letters. Eighty-two three-dimensional objects designed by Fabres are held by the Society's Museum.</p>
        </relatedmaterial>
